{"type": "article", "id": 8045, "title": "Chloe Wise 大牌面“包”", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-02T07:44:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234647Wn79kMD1QKTvIVEo.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t你来看看这个到底是面包还是包包？其实都不是啦，这是设计师 Chloe Wise 的面包雕塑作品。从去年开始，这位来自加拿大的俏皮设计师就一直在醉心于把各种大牌的包包做成面包的模样，品牌涉及到 LV，Chanel，Prada，Coach 等等，以此来挑战艺术和时尚的界限。去年 India Muenez 背着一款 Chanel Bagel No.5 出席 Chanel 纽约大 Party，时尚界甚至有人“预言”这种“包”将会成为未来的一股新潮流，这个幽默风趣的女孩听了乐得直躲在后面偷笑。这里是之前<a href=\"http://www.galeriedivision.com/montreal/exhibitions\" target=\"_blank\">她做展览的链接</a>。你买不到这些包包，但这个是别的食物饰品的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/196156201/polymer-clay-cream-cheese-bagel-necklace?ref=sr_gallery_5&amp;ga_search_query=bagel+necklace&amp;ga_search_type=all&amp;ga_view_type=gallery\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>，感兴趣可以进来看看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052346441IgKnLquj6hBoraU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.98899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234644COZqyb6xlfU4KGpn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0403423\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234645qtIdnkVlQ2oRfGj3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.9400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234645T5vUxEtKRd2o1ZgC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.07212714\" data-fo